values:
I don't have to think. I only have to do it. 
You get lyrics tonight, because I felt I should update, but I have but nothing to say. A dollar to anyone who can name the song I was singing while I wrote that first line.
Enjoy.
Voice is gone. Excellent. Presentation due tomorrow afternoon.
Happy Valentine's day. What better time of year to have a crippling ear infection and stomach ailment. Nothin' says lovin' like a toilet full of my vomit.

Today I cleaned my bathroom decorations. A soap dish in the shape of a bath tub, and a toothbrush holder in the shape of a sink. They're remarkably clever. 
I brushed my teeth  before bed, and I set my toothbrush on the counter. Not in the toothbrush holder... I cannot imagine what must have been going through my mind at the time.
